#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Choosing a GraalVM distribution"
msgstr "选择 GraalVM 发行版"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Building a native executable requires a GraalVM distribution. There are two main options:"
msgstr "要构建原生可执行文件，需要一个 GraalVM 发行版。主要有两种选择："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*https://www.graalvm.org[Oracle GraalVM]* — the standard distribution from Oracle. Supports Linux, macOS (both Intel and Apple Silicon), and Windows."
msgstr "*link:https://www.graalvm.org[Oracle GraalVM]* —— Oracle 提供的标准发行版。支持 Linux、macOS（包括 Intel 和 Apple Silicon 架构）以及 Windows。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*https://github.com/graalvm/mandrel[Mandrel]* — a downstream distribution tailored for Quarkus. It excludes components not needed by Quarkus (such as polyglot support) to provide a smaller distribution."
msgstr "*link:https://github.com/graalvm/mandrel[Mandrel]* ——一个专为 Quarkus 量身定制的下游发行版。它排除了 Quarkus 不需要的组件（例如多语言支持），从而提供了更精简的发行版。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "GraalVM {graalvm-version} is required."
msgstr "需要 GraalVM {graalvm-version}。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Configuring GraalVM"
msgstr "配置GraalVM"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This step is only required for generating native executables targeting non-Linux operating systems.\n"
"For generating native executables targeting Linux, you can optionally skip this section and <<#container-runtime,use a builder image>> instead."
msgstr "此步骤仅在生成面向非 Linux 操作系统的原生可执行文件时才需要。若要生成面向 Linux 的原生可执行文件，您可以选择跳过本节，转而 xref:container-runtime[使用构建镜像] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you cannot install GraalVM, you can use a multi-stage Docker build to run Maven inside a Docker container that embeds GraalVM.\n"
"There is an explanation of how to do this in the xref:native-reference.adoc#multistage-docker[Native Reference Guide]."
msgstr "如果无法安装 GraalVM，您可以使用多阶段 Docker 构建，在嵌有 GraalVM 的 Docker 容器中运行 Maven。《 xref:native-reference.adoc#multistage-docker[原生参考指南》] 中对此操作方法进行了说明。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
msgid "Install GraalVM if you haven't already. You have a few options for this:"
msgstr "如果你还没有安装 GraalVM。那么你有几个选择："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Download the appropriate archive from <https://github.com/graalvm/mandrel/releases> or <https://www.graalvm.org/downloads/>, and unpack it like you would any other JDK."
msgstr "请从 https://github.com/graalvm/mandrel/releases 或 https://www.graalvm.org/downloads/ 下载相应的压缩包，并像安装其他 JDK 一样将其解压。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Use platform-specific installer tools like https://sdkman.io/jdks#graalce[sdkman], https://github.com/graalvm/homebrew-tap[homebrew], or https://github.com/ScoopInstaller/Java[scoop].\n"
"For example, install it with `sdk install java {graalvm-flavor}`."
msgstr "使用平台专用的安装工具，例如 link:https://sdkman.io/jdks#graalce[sdkman] 、 link:https://github.com/graalvm/homebrew-tap[homebrew] 或 link:https://github.com/ScoopInstaller/Java[scoop] 。例如，可通过以下命令进行安装： `sdk install java {graalvm-flavor}` 。"

