#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Producing a native executable"
msgstr "制作一个原生可执行文件"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The native executable for your application will contain the application code, required libraries, Java APIs, and a reduced version of a VM.\n"
"The smaller VM base improves the startup time of the application and produces a minimal disk footprint."
msgstr "您应用程序的原生可执行文件将包含应用程序代码、所需的库、Java API 以及一个精简版的虚拟机。更小的虚拟机基础部分可缩短应用程序的启动时间，并最大限度地减少磁盘占用空间。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
msgid "image:native-executable-process.png[Creating a native executable]"
msgstr "image:native-executable-process.png[创建原生可执行文件]"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can provide custom options for the `native-image` command using the `quarkus.native.additional-build-args` and `quarkus.native.additional-build-args-append` properties.\n"
"Multiple options may be separated by a comma."
msgstr "您可以使用 `quarkus.native.additional-build-args` 和 `quarkus.native.additional-build-args-append` 属性为 `native-image` 命令提供自定义选项。多个选项可用逗号分隔。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
msgid "You can find more information about how to configure the native image building process in the <<configuration-reference>> section below."
msgstr "你可以在下面的 <<configuration-reference>> 部分找到关于如何配置原生镜像构建过程的更多信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Native compilation takes significantly longer than a regular JVM build. Create a native executable using:"
msgstr "本机编译所需的时间远比常规的 JVM 构建要长。请使用以下命令创建本机可执行文件："

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Issues with packaging on Windows"
msgstr "在Windows上打包的问题"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Microsoft Native Tools for Visual Studio must first be initialized before packaging.\n"
"You can do this by starting the `x64 Native Tools Command Prompt` that was installed with the Visual Studio Build Tools.\n"
"At the `x64 Native Tools Command Prompt`, you can navigate to your project folder and run `./mvnw package -Dnative`."
msgstr "在打包之前，必须先初始化 Visual Studio 的 Microsoft 本机工具。您可以通过启动随 Visual Studio 构建工具一起安装的 `x64 本机工具命令提示符` 来完成此操作。在 `x64 本机工具命令提示符下` ，您可以导航至项目文件夹，然后运行 `./mvnw package -Dnative。`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The build produces `target/getting-started-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT-runner`.\n"
"You can run it directly:"
msgstr "构建后会生成 `target/getting-started-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT-runner` 。您可以直接运行它："

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Testing the native executable"
msgstr "测试原生可执行文件"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Producing a native executable can lead to a few issues, and so it's also a good idea to run some tests against the application running in the native file.\n"
"The reasoning is explained in the xref:getting-started-testing.adoc#quarkus-integration-test[Testing Guide]."
msgstr "生成原生可执行文件可能会引发一些问题，因此，对在原生文件中运行的应用程序进行一些测试也是个好主意。具体原因在《 xref:getting-started-testing.adoc#quarkus-integration-test[测试指南] 》中进行了说明。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To see the `GreetingResourceIT` run against the native executable, use `./mvnw verify -Dnative`:"
msgstr "要查看 `GreetingResourceIT` 在本机可执行文件上运行的情况，请使用 `./mvnw verify -Dnative` ："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By default, Quarkus waits for 60 seconds for the native image to start before automatically failing the native tests. This\n"
"duration can be changed using the `quarkus.test.wait-time` system property. For example, to increase the duration\n"
"to 300 seconds, use: `./mvnw verify -Dnative -Dquarkus.test.wait-time=300`."
msgstr "默认情况下，Quarkus 会等待 60 秒，看原生映像是否启动，之后才会自动判定原生测试失败。可以通过 `quarkus.test.wait-time` 系统属性来更改此等待时长。 例如，若要将等待时间延长至 300 秒，请使用： `./mvnw verify -Dnative -Dquarkus.test.wait-time=300` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For advanced testing scenarios, test profiles, excluding tests from native runs, or testing an existing binary, see the xref:native-reference.adoc#native-testing[Native Reference Guide]."
msgstr "有关高级测试场景、测试配置文件、从原生运行中排除测试，或对现有二进制文件进行测试，请参阅《 xref:native-reference.adoc#native-testing[原生参考指南] 》。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Creating a Linux executable without GraalVM installed"
msgstr "在没有安装GraalVM的情况下创建一个Linux可执行文件"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
msgid ""
"Before going further, be sure to have a working container runtime (Docker, podman) environment.\n"
"If you use Docker on Windows you should share your project's drive at Docker Desktop file share settings and restart Docker Desktop."
msgstr "在进一步行动之前，请确保有一个工作的容器运行环境（Docker或podman）。如果你在Windows上使用Docker，你应该在Docker Desktop文件共享设置中共享你的项目的驱动器，并重新启动Docker Desktop。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
msgid ""
"Quite often one only needs to create a native Linux executable for their Quarkus application (for example in order to run in a containerized environment) and would like to avoid\n"
"the trouble of installing the proper GraalVM version in order to accomplish this task (for example, in CI environments it's common practice\n"
"to install as little software as possible)."
msgstr "很多时候，人们只需要为他们的Quarkus应用程序创建一个原生Linux可执行文件（例如，为了在容器化环境中运行），并希望避免安装适当的GraalVM版本来完成这项麻烦任务（例如，在CI环境中，通常的做法是尽可能少地安装软件）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
msgid ""
"To this end, Quarkus provides a very convenient way of creating a native Linux executable by leveraging a container runtime such as Docker or podman.\n"
"The easiest way of accomplishing this task is to execute:"
msgstr "为此，Quarkus提供了一个非常方便的方法，通过利用容器运行时（如Docker或podman）来创建一个原生Linux可执行文件。完成这项任务的最简单方法是执行："

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "What to expect"
msgstr "可以期待什么"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Your first container-based native build typically takes 3-10 minutes and uses 4-8 GB of RAM on the build host.\n"
"Fan spin-up is normal; the build is still running, just working hard.\n"
"A build that runs past 15 minutes without output usually means the container runtime is short on memory; raise its CPU and memory allocation and retry."
msgstr "首次基于容器的原生构建通常需要 3 到 10 分钟，并在构建主机上占用 4 到 8 GB 的内存。风扇转速加快是正常现象；这说明构建仍在进行中，只是正在全力运行。 如果构建运行超过 15 分钟却没有输出，通常意味着容器运行时内存不足；请增加其 CPU 和内存分配，然后重试。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The output is a Linux binary produced inside the builder image.\n"
"Its architecture matches the builder image you pulled: typically `x86_64` unless you explicitly selected an `arm64` variant or are running on an `arm64` host.\n"
"Run the binary in a Linux container that matches that architecture, not directly on your host OS."
msgstr "输出结果是在构建镜像内部生成的 Linux 二进制文件。其架构与您拉取的构建镜像一致：通常 `为 x86_64，` 除非您明确选择了 `arm64` 变体，或者正在 `arm64` 主机上运行。请在与该架构匹配的 Linux 容器中运行该二进制文件，不要直接在您的主机操作系统上运行。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
msgid ""
"By default, Quarkus automatically detects the container runtime.\n"
"If you want to explicitly select the container runtime, you can do it with:"
msgstr "默认情况下，Quarkus会自动检测容器的运行时。如果你想显式指定择容器的运行时，你可以通过以下方式实现："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
msgid "For Docker:"
msgstr "对于Docker："

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "CLI"
msgstr "CLI"

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
msgid "Maven"
msgstr "Maven"

#. type: Block title
