msgid "Gradle"
msgstr "Gradle"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
msgid "For podman:"
msgstr "对于podman："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"These are regular Quarkus config properties, so if you always want to build in a container\n"
"it is recommended you add these to your `application.properties` in order to avoid specifying them every time."
msgstr "这些是常规的 Quarkus 配置属性，因此，如果您希望始终在容器中进行构建，建议将这些属性添加到 `application.properties` 文件中，以免每次都需要手动指定。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Executable built that way with the container runtime will be a 64-bit Linux executable, so depending on your operating system, it may no longer be runnable."
msgstr "使用容器运行时以这种方式构建的可执行文件将是一个 64 位 Linux 可执行文件，因此根据您所使用的操作系统不同，它可能无法再运行。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The _builder_ image used to build the native executable is based on UBI 10.\n"
"It means that the native executable produced by the container build will be based on UBI 10 as well.\n"
"So, if you plan to build a container, make sure that the base image in your `Dockerfile` is compatible with UBI 10.\n"
"The native executable will not run on UBI 8 or UBI 9 base images."
msgstr "用于构建原生可执行文件的 _构建镜像_ 基于 UBI 10。这意味着通过容器构建生成的原生可执行文件也将基于 UBI 10。 因此，如果您计划构建一个容器，请确保 `Dockerfile` 中的基础镜像与 UBI 10 兼容。原生可执行文件无法在 UBI 8 或 UBI 9 基础镜像上运行。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
